# This file indicates that the bot is running in local development mode
# Copy this file to the root directory as ".local_marker" (without the .example extension)
# When this file exists, the bot will:
# - Deploy commands to a specific guild (specified by GUILD_ID in .env)
# - Enable local-only debugging features
#
# To use:
# 1. Create a file named ".local_marker" in the root directory (leave it empty)
# 2. The bot will automatically detect it and enable local development mode
